The rest of the article is organized as follows:
First, in Section~\ref{sec:acquisition}, we describe the acquisition and processing of the raw audiovisual data. Next, in Section~\ref{sec:opening-speech-and-closing-segment}, we describe the preparation of the video recording of the opening speech and the closing segment of the performance. Then, in Section~\ref{sec:panels}, we describe the preparation of the panels accompanying the performance. Finally, in Section~\ref{sec:final-video-assembly}, we describe how the individual parts were combined into the final recording. In Section~\ref{sec:conclusion}, we describe the screening of the finished video recording at \acro{FI~MU} on December~18, 2019.
